       | Power:Ground |

       #+------------+------------+----------+------------+-----------+--------+--------------+

       #| metal1     | 42         | 0        |  0%          |  0          |  0
       | 0:0          |

       #|  metal3      |  28          | 11       | 39%        | 0         | 11
       | 0:11         |

       #+------------+------------+----------+------------+-----------+--------+--------------+

       #| Total      | 70         | 11       | 15%         |  0          |  11
       | 0:11         |

       #+------------+------------+----------+------------+-----------+--------+--------------+

       The following command prints a detailed report in myDesign_shield_2.rpt
       file  without  breaking down by segment. This command is called without
       the -verbose option.

       reportShield -crosstie -selected -out_file myDesign_shield_2.rpt

